00:32:21.130 --> 00:32:23.280
street, but in downtown where
there's a grocery store where

00:32:23.280 --> 00:32:24.380
used to go all the time.

00:32:24.380 --> 00:32:26.635
And I was just driving down
there last week, and I

00:32:26.635 --> 00:32:28.880
thought, man, I haven't been to
that grocery store in-- and

00:32:28.880 --> 00:32:30.920
then I start counting, and I
said-- six years since we

00:32:30.920 --> 00:32:32.180
opened Myers and Chang.

00:32:32.180 --> 00:32:35.030
There's really no reason
for me to cook.

00:32:35.030 --> 00:32:37.970
I enjoy it, but it's so easy
just to go to the restaurant

00:32:37.970 --> 00:32:39.670
to get take out and
bring it home.

00:32:39.670 --> 00:32:41.815
So we do a lot of that.

00:32:41.815 --> 00:32:44.220
SANDRA LEUNG LI: And so you must
be an expert, obviously,

00:32:44.220 --> 00:32:46.030
on all the dishes at
Myers and Chang--

00:32:46.030 --> 00:32:46.530
JOANNE CHANG: Oh, yeah.

00:32:46.530 --> 00:32:47.150
SANDRA LEUNG LI: --with
the take out.

00:32:47.150 --> 00:32:49.780
What do you usually take out?

00:32:49.780 --> 00:32:50.320
JOANNE CHANG: Let's see.

00:32:50.320 --> 00:32:52.650
We get the salmon.

00:32:52.650 --> 00:32:56.380
It's a pan-roasted,
soy-glazed salmon.

00:32:56.380 --> 00:32:57.930
It's very, very simple.

00:32:57.930 --> 00:32:59.760
It's definitely not the dish
that I recommend when I'm

00:32:59.760 --> 00:33:02.260
trying to show off about what
Myers and Chang is all about,

00:33:02.260 --> 00:33:03.740
but it's my favorite dish.

00:33:03.740 --> 00:33:05.670
It's really simple
and delicious.

00:33:05.670 --> 00:33:06.850
We get the lamb belly.

00:33:06.850 --> 00:33:10.370
It's a lamb belly stir-fry with
slippery glass noodles

00:33:10.370 --> 00:33:14.270
and leeks and sesame seeds.

00:33:14.270 --> 00:33:18.880
The spicy salmon and apple
tartare with sesame crisps is

00:33:18.880 --> 00:33:20.140
one of my favorites.

00:33:20.140 --> 00:33:21.350
We always get a vegetable.

00:33:21.350 --> 00:33:22.320
Yeah.

00:33:22.320 --> 00:33:24.510
SANDRA LEUNG LI: Sounds good.

