I don't listen to music.

00:34:21.980 --> 00:34:24.100
In fact, last night driving out
to Wellesley, I thought, I

00:34:24.100 --> 00:34:26.040
should turn on the radio just
to see, what are people

00:34:26.040 --> 00:34:27.590
listening to these days?

