I don't even know what
playlist means.

00:34:30.739 --> 00:34:31.570
I don't listen at all.

00:34:31.570 --> 00:34:36.880
I used to listen to a hip hop
station, pop station, KISS

00:34:36.880 --> 00:34:38.810
108, because I used to
run to headphones.

00:34:38.810 --> 00:34:41.340
And then my headphones got
stolen three years ago, and I

00:34:41.340 --> 00:34:44.030
just stopped listening.

